fields.crisis_title: Bombing at Clarke Quay MRT Station
Riot near Ang Mo Kio Hub
Child kidnapped in Woodlands Post Office
This crisis is without action plans

fields.description: Fire is seen around Esplanade Area.
Full chaos near Esplanade MRT
One terrorist has kidnapped a child during this chaos at esplanade area.
Sudden explosion of bomb is audible at the esplanade building engulfed in flames.
I just heard a bomb exploding from Clarke Quay Central.
The bomb has caused a fire around clarke quay area.
People are running around and full chaos here after the first bomb exploded and the fear of second one going to explode soon.
There is a bomb detected at clarke quay mrt station that is going to explode in 2 hours.
There is an ongoing bomb situation.
Help la FML
FML

fire in the zoo
fire lor

Huge fire and fumes at Esplanade building.
4-5 people are stuck inside still.

1 person might still be stuck inside the top storey of the building. 
Request for the whole team of EF to come down and assist with the situation.

Building is burning with fire non-stop with casualties.
Request entire fire dept team to come down urgently.
Bombing near Eu Tong Sen Street. Request SAF team to come immediately.
There are no casualties as of now but request whole SAF team to come down just in case another bomb explosion occurs.
5 people have been injured by the previous bomb at Clarke Quay and another bomb has been detected there. Request SAF bomb squad team to come down and defuse it.
Buses have been set on fire in Ang Mo Kio Interchange, possibility of some people accidentally getting hurt. Request SPF and SCDF to attend to the situation immediately.
Some people are fighting with each other in AMK Hub. Request all forces to attend the situation.
Some people are destroying the public property in AMK Hub as well as breaking down the buses in interchange violently. Requesting SAF forces to help urgently.
A child has been kidnapped in Woodlands Post Office and kidnapper is demanding ransom of $100,000 from parents. Requesting entire team of SPF to attend this case.
Child kidnapped in Woodlands Post Office. Requesting a few personnel from SPF to attend the case first.

Kidnapped child has been safely returned to his parents. Kidnapper along with his gang of criminals on wanted list are in SPF's custody, a few more personnel needed to handle the criminals there and bring them to station.
A protest is occurring at Central Area against PAP. Some people have fainted. Requesting SCDF to attend to these people.
Cars are being broken in the CBD area and heavy fires are being started. Requesting SCDF at once to handle this situation.
Riot has been brought under control but need forces to clean up the area and damage done there.

fields.description: 5 people are stuck in the building. Request for extra personnel to help the situation.
Managed to get the 5 people out of the building, but they are slightly injured/bruised. They have been brought to the hospital already.
The five casualties are taking treatment at the hospital. Doctors have said no serious harm to their health. Crowd has been controlled at esplanade but fire is still being put off.
We have just seen the bomb and trying to defuse it. Request more forces to calm the residents.
Successfully defused the bomb. The panic of residents have been controlled. Still awaiting information from the hospital regarding the patients' current condition.
2 out of the 5 people admitted to the hospital have lost a leg. Meanwhile we are still searching the place for any other hidden bombs.
Trying to track location of kidnappers through GPS.
Kidnappers' location have been found. Child is safe and back to parents. Surrounded kidnappers with the limited personnel we have. Need more to bring the whole lot to station.
Gang has been brought to station and interrogated in the appropriate way. Situation under control.
Situation is under control now. Need more personnel to clean up the place.
